    "description": "<p>Big Sailing International (Foodmax) originated from Dingdong Maicai (NYSE: DDL), China's leading fresh food retail platform. Founded in May 2017 and headquartered in Shanghai, China, Foodmax is a fresh food supply chain company focused on delicious food. We provide global customers with food supply chain services including direct sourcing from the source, cross-border customs clearance, product development, warehousing and processing, cold chain logistics, and sales services.</p>",
